name: Defense of Muunilinst
Text: 'Deploy on War Has Begun. Unless a card stacked here, if you control three Muunilinst locations (and opponent controls no Muunilinst locations), opponent loses 1 Force (cannot be reduced) and stacks lost card here face down (Mission ''complete'').Reward: Your Force drains at Muunilinst locations are +1 and, once per turn, may raise your converted Muunilinst site to the top.Turn The Tide: If opponent controls two Muunilinst locations, place Mission in Used Pile.',
